# This directory stores uploaded license plate images.
# Images are stored here by Django's ImageField (PlateDetectionEvent.image).
# The directory is tracked in git via this .gitkeep file, but the images
# themselves are excluded by .gitignore (they're user-generated content,
# not application code).
#
# In Docker, this directory is mounted as a named volume ('media') so uploaded
# images persist across container restarts. See docker-compose.yml.
#
# The cleanup_old_images management command (Day 11) reads LotSettings.image_retention_days
# and deletes images older than that threshold from this directory.
